name: Artbreeder+
description:
Browser addon that expands and enhances the website https://artbreeder.com.

This addon was made for the old version of the website, it wont work for the new one.

I originally just made this as an addon for myself, that could display the amount of likes/hearts an image has received, as that was included the the json file image requests , but was unused and not displayed.

I later added a bunch of other features to the addon and published it to addons.mozilla.org.

Small warning, if anyone wants to look into the code...
It's a total mess.
